Package claudiosoft.jarbox

Class ContentEntry

java.lang.Object
java.util.zip.ZipEntry
claudiosoft.jarbox.ContentEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class ContentEntry
extends ZipEntry
A single JarBox's entry, deployed inside user temporary folder. A "core" entry isn't included under job or context folder and it is locked by file system. Every entry has a status SHA256 hash
